title: Gisele Bundchen: ON Being Kinder To Yourself
description: Gisele’s wisdom goes deep - from reading the Bhagavad Gita between breaks on the runway to falling in love with discipline in her childhood, you’ll be able to tell immediately there’s much more to her than just being one of the world’s most famous supermodels.
author: onpurposepodcast@jayshetty.me (Jay Shetty)
